https://console.groq.com/docs/quickstart.text:
1. To get started with the Groq API, create an API Key by visiting the provided link.

2. Set up your API Key as an environment variable for streamlined usage and enhanced security.

3. Install the Groq Python library using pip install groq.

4. Perform a chat completion using the Groq API by importing the Groq library, setting up a client with your API key, and creating a chat completion request with a sample message.

5. Check out the Playground to try out the Groq API in your browser.

6. Join the GroqCloud developer community on Discord for further assistance and discussions.

7. Use the Groq API to chat with Docs at lightning speed.

8. Add a how-to on your project to the Groq API Cookbook for sharing knowledge and best practices.
